container.value: Office 85 2 Old Brompton Road, London, England, SW7 3DQ

creator: JoyBits Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Solve brain teasers in Pin puzzle games.

Help brave sandfish and the girl overcome all the traps in this pin puzzle games! Are you smart enough to solve these brain teaser tests in order to save the fish and his girl from the shark chasing them! Make the right choices and lead the fish and the girl to safety.

Dive into the most addicting pin puzzle games ever! Have fun solving funny and difficult problems with the pines and the pins. Use your brains and go get to solving!

Game Features:
- Make right choices!
Each level presents you with multiple choices. Wrong answers will result in painful but funny outcomes to the fish!

- Are into pulling the pins?
Here you will find the best pin puzzle games ever!

- Many levels to play
And many different challenges for you to solve.

- Save not the fish only
You should save the girl as well.

An incredible game where you need to save a small fish.
Go along with the fish through amazing puzzles and help the fish to get home.
Use your brain to solve the puzzles and enjoy yourself. 
If you are a big fan of pin puzzle games, saving games, brain teasers, or just want to check your iQ, then save the fish and help the girl!
descriptionShort: Solve pin puzzle games in fish rescue adventure! Pull the pins to save the Fish.

title: Save the Fish・Pin puzzle Games

container.value: Office 85 2 Old Brompton Road, London, England, SW7 3DQ

creator: JoyBits Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Solve brain teasers in Pin puzzle games.

Help the brave Neptune and a Fish overcome all the traps in these puzzle games! Solve these puzzles to save the Fish and Neptune from chasing sharks and sly mermaids? Make the right choice and bring Seafish and Neptune to safety.


Dive into the most addicting pin puzzle games ever! Have fun solving funny and difficult problems with the pines and the pins. Use your brains and go get to solving!

Game Features:
- Make right choices!
Each level presents you with multiple choices. Wrong answers will result in painful but funny outcomes to the fish!

- Are into pulling the pins?
Here you will find the best pin puzzle games ever!

- Many levels to play
And many different challenges for you to solve.

- Save not the fish only
You should save the girl as well.

An incredible game where you need to save a small fish.
Go along with the fish through amazing puzzles and help the fish to get home.
Use your brain to solve the puzzles and enjoy yourself. 
If you are a big fan of pin puzzle games, saving games, brain teasers, or just want to check your iQ, then save the fish and help the girl!
descriptionShort: Solve pin puzzle games in fish rescue adventure! Pull the pins to save the Fish.

descriptionHtml:
They are very mischievous and try various things every day!

However, mischief should never be caught.
Let's secretly and carefully set up a prank on the people in the underwater city!
When the mischief is successful, you will find it fun enough to start dancing!

Addictive free tricky puzzle game including many fun mini games. This funny puzzle game is the story about an underwater world. You need to master your brain to rescue the fish princess, pass all obstacles and escape from the shark.

Help the brave Neptune and a Fish overcome all the traps in these puzzle games! Solve these puzzles to save the Fish and Neptune from chasing sharks and sly mermaids? Make the right choice and bring Seafish and Neptune to safety.

Let's relieve stress by having a lot of mischievous experiences in the game that will make you really angry in reality!

⭐️FEATURES⭐️
⚡ Synced sound, flash and vibration.
⚡ Excellent option for pranking.
⚡ Unique and creative game modes
⚡ 100% free game, play it anywhere anytime
⚡ No time limit, just enjoy!
⚡ One finger control
⚡ For kids and adults

⭐️GAME MODES⭐️
⚡ Choice puzzle: choose the right answers to save the little fish.
⚡ Pull the pin: Pull the correct pins to escape from sharks and rescue the fish princess.
⚡ Flappy Fish: tap on the screen to help the fish pass obstacles.
⚡ Pipe puzzle: Use your brain to arrange the pipes to get the fish and his lover
⚡ Chat text: Fill the right texts to create humorous conversations
⚡ Phone and Tablet support
⚡ Beware of sharks!

Be the smartest in the ocean!
descriptionShort: Neptune and his fish friends do pranks on girls they like. Dodge their pranks!
